00:24:26.731 --> 00:24:30.802
How Embracing Accessibility
Made Me a Better Storyteller."

00:24:30.835 --> 00:24:32.337
I know I'm excited for that.

00:24:32.370 --> 00:24:33.671
I just attended the
STORY Gatherings

00:24:33.704 --> 00:24:35.173
